steps.name: New User Setup: Free User Sign up
Free user sign up API call
New User Setup: Free User Email Confirmation via Database
New User Setup: Free User Login
New User Setup: Upgrade Free User to Business
Click on "Settings" item on the left SideMenu
Click on "Billing" item in the Settings SubMenu
Click "No,thanks" button on the One Time Special Offer Modal
The toast message with the text "Plan has been successfully changed." is visible and then hidden
Click on "Sign" item on the left SideMenu
Precondition: Document creation in progress with Awaiting status
Select the "Send for Signature" radio button.
Fill the name of the signer into the "Name" input field.
Fill the email address of the signer into the "Email" input field.
Click on the "Send for Signature" button.
The toast message with the text "Document successfully saved!" is visible and then hidden
Click on the "Back to Documents" button.
Click on "Sign" item on the left SideMenu
Click on "Documents" item on the left SideMenu
Select the "Edit & Resend" option in the dropdown menu
Verify that the editing window is open
